      • getTransparency

        Transparency getTransparency()
        Gets the transparency object and the color interpretation of the result. Mostly, filters returns ARGB images but sometimes the filter can alterate the transparency configuration and the color interpretation. For instance, when a color table is applied or a alpha band is added by the filter.
